Looking at daily shifts among states can contextualize the broad shifts in intensity across phases seen above. Three metrics in particular are useful: daily shift among states; observed variation of confirmed cases with respect to in-shifts and out-shifts; and daily costs of shifts as a measure of severity of the pandemic in states. These metrics give insight into the nature of how the pandemic plays out over time.Figure 2
